  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Savoy Edelweiss is the perfect little place if you're after and home-away-from-home feel. There's only 30 rooms and a comfy, mountain-style décor. The staff are all fantastic too and will make sure you have a great stay. </p>
<p>The location's ideal for keen skiers. The lifts are a two-minute walk away and you can handily store your skis in the ski deposit (da Rosanna) near the piste. That means you're free to enjoy the après scene after skiing. When you get back to the hotel, you can look forward to a filling four-course dinner before settling in for the night.</p>]]></description>
