  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms </strong>are about 11-15m² and sleep two people.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> are about 20-24m² and sleep up to four people (extra beds are single beds).</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Twin Rooms</strong> are about 12-16m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Plus Rooms</strong> are about 18m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single bed). They have a bath with overhead shower and have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Double Rooms for single use </strong>are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p>Mountain view rooms can be requested at the time of booking but they cannot be guaranteed.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Mini fridge</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
